I";<h1 id="collaboration">Collaboration</h1>

<p>We are placed in the <a href="https://www.iitg.ac.in/dsai/">Mehta Family School of Data Science and AI</a>, Indian Institute of Technology, Guwahati. Alongside exercising our brains, we enjoy discussing and working with individuals (and groups) with interests in solving interesting and impactful problems. Feel free to send us an <a href="mailto:neerajs@iitg.ac.in">email</a> if you think together we can make an impact.</p>

<h4 id="academic">Academic</h4>
<p>We exchange ideas and work with our neighbors from Dept. EEE and Center for Linguistic Science and Technology. Outside campus, we enjoy sharing knowledge and working with <a href="http://leap.ee.iisc.ac.in/sriram/">Sriram Ganapathy</a> (and <a href="http://leap.ee.iisc.ac.in/">LEAP Lab</a>) at the Indian Institute of Science, Bangalore and <a href="https://www.audiolabs-erlangen.de/fau/professor/habets">Emanuel Habets</a> (and the <a href="https://www.audiolabs-erlangen.de/">International Audio Labs</a>) at Fraunhofer IIS, Erlangen.</p>

<h4 id="industry">Industry</h4>
<p>Our research is always motivated with an engineering use case. If you are from domains like</p>
<ul>
  <li>audio signal processing</li>
  <li>deep learning and AI for human machine communication</li>
  <li>brain computer interfacing</li>
  <li>signal processing for automotive</li>
</ul>

<p>and will like to discuss options for collaboration, feel free to send us an <a href="mailto:neerajs@iitg.ac.in">email</a>. Further, in case you wish to sponsor utilities as we setup our new lab, you are welcome!!</p>

<h4 id="outreach">Outreach</h4>
<p>Let us know by <a href="mailto:neerajs@iitg.ac.in">email</a> if you would like us to share ``about our research at your School/College/Institute. We will try to see if we can fit the opportunity into our schedule.</p>

